content: simpletrontdip: Merged a significant PR (#1229) that added Markdown parsing mode and enhanced telegram bot output, involving substantial code changes (+24,319/-18,720 lines). Currently has two open PRs (#1263 and #1366) focused on enhancing the birdeye provider to support all possible EVM symbols. Contributed actively to the project through code reviews, providing 3 reviews (1 approval, 2 comments) and 7 PR comments, despite being active on only 2 days this month.
